name: Elizabeth Pochhammer
biography: Born Elizabeth Wilken in Germany. Active in Berlin from 1864-1880. Married Dr. Med. Edmund von Pochhammer, court physician in Potsdam.  See Hessisches Landesamt fur geschichtliche Landeskunde http://lagis-hessen.de/de/subjects/rsrec/sn/bio/register/person/entry/... (This information obtained by Gail Davidson during visit to state drawings collections, Potsdam, May 2015)
